high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the counter, then turn right and walk up to the black table.
Pick up the tomato off of the black table.
Turn right and walk towards the white table, then hang a right and walk up to the stove and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside, then close the microwave door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the tomato then close the door.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the black shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the heated tomato on top of the black shelving unit in between the mug and apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on top of a black shelving unit.

high_descs: grab the tomato on the table
turn around, walk to the stove
open the microwave above, put the tomato in , cook it for a while, take the tomato out
turn around, walk to the shelf in the corner on the right
put the tomato on the shelf
anns.task_desc: cook the tomato in the microwave, put the tomato on the corner shelf

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the tomato from near the middle of the table.
Turn right and walk until you're even with the stove on your right then turn right and walk to the stove.
Cook the tomato in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the table.
Put the tomato to the left of the coffee mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato on the table.
